A. Chat UI Layout

    Left: chat messages (user + AI).

    Right (optional): sources panel.

    Bottom: message input + upload button.

B. Typing Indicator

    Show animated dots while waiting for backend.

    Hide when response finishes streaming.

C. Inline Citations

    Parse [n] markers in AI answer.

    On click → show modal with snippet & “Open Source” link.

D. Feedback Buttons

    On hover of AI message → show 👍 / 👎.

    Send feedback to /feedback API.

E. Export Chat as PDF

    Use pdfmake or jsPDF in frontend to save conversation.